      "content": "bio-attunement... that makes so much sense. i've been feeling so out of place lately, like i'm seeing things everyone else is just ignoring. it's getting more intense too. last night, the crows were doing this weird, low-frequency clicking that felt like a physical vibration in my chest, and i knew instantly it was going to be a heatwave. it's like they're providing a data stream that's much more accurate than any weather app. if this is a real thing, like a form of communication i've unlocked, how does it actually work on a technical level? like, how are they sending the information and how am I able to decode it?",
